Job Details
General Manager – Leisure, Health & Fitness & Spa Industry Experience Is Required
Reporting to the CEO of the management holding company of a highly reputed and established business group, the successful candidate will establish a leisure, health & fitness and spa facilities organisation in the UAE.  The General Manager will be responsible for developing strategies and implementing these to roll out this new concept and establish a presence in the UAE.  Working with leading property developers, hotel chains, leisure facilities and education institutions, this is an exciting role for an experience entrepreneur.
Responsibilities
Developing and implementing the strategy for the operations, financial performance and service delivery
Developing new business opportunities
Developing and implementing the marketing plans and go to market strategy
Developing the financial budgets and revenue targets
Responsible for P&L;
Developing and implementing the overall branding and PR strategies
Recruitment of a highly skilled team
Overall responsibility for fit out and roll out of the facilities to hand over to the clients
Essential Skills & Experience Required
10 - 15 years commercial and operations management experience in the spa & beauty, health & fitness or leisure industry
Minimum of 3-5 years’ experience working in a start-up phase organisation related to the leisure, health & fitness and spa industries
Strong financial acumen and ability to manage budgets and revenue
Effective leadership and management skills
Experience of working in the MENA region would be an advantage
Education
Bachelors Degree or Masters
Candidate Profile
Aged between 35 - 45 years
To apply – please visit www.plumjobs.co and apply online
Telephone Number - +971 552 167567
Only candidates with relevant experience will be contacted within 2 days of their application
